6
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:20,680
Suit each other?

7
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,440
No way.

8
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,320
Bullshit.

9
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:30,040
