can't stand her being with someone else.

11
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,320
Lao Wen.

12
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,000
Aren't you contradicting yourself?

13
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:41,120
You're the one who always finds ways
to hide from me.

14
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,760
But you're also the one who wants
to wander around the world with me.

15
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,920
Aren't you contradicting yourself?

16
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,960
Let me ask you.

17
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:51,760
When you were coaxing
Cao Weining just now,

18
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,280
which words of yours are true?

19
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,200
Which are not?

20
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,080
Some of them are true, some are not.

21
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,200
Take a guess.

22
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,600
CHONGWU PALACE

23
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:13,160
A thousand feet deep
The Peach Blossom Lake may be

24
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,960
It could not compare
With Wang Lun's love for me

25
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,120
What is love supposed to be?

26
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:20,320
Why would lovers die for it?

27
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:23,720
What phrases are you mumbling?

28
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:27,240
Ah Xiang, I'm feeling emotional.

29
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:30,400
Life is too short,
so live it to the fullest.

30
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:33,440
Look, how lucky are Mr. Zhou and Mr. Wen

31
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,640
to become soul mates

32
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:36,600
and go through thin and thick together.

33
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:41,520
But too bad that the heavens
are playing with them.

34
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,960
Mr. Zhou is severely ill.

35
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:47,240
If he passes away one day,

36
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:49,800
Mr. Wen will lose his soul mate.

37
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,960
Why are you worrying about him?

38
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:56,240
He can't just stay
with a guy forever, right?

39
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,480
You're wrong.

40
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,280
Ah Xiang.

41
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,200
Let me tell you a story.

42
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:04,400
-I don't want to hear it.
-I want to tell you.

43
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:10,880
My Master Fan

44
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,600
is a handsome man,

45
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,960
but he has never married.

46
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,240
I was naive when I was little

47
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:18,160
and asked him why he didn't marry.

48
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,560
He told me,

49
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:23,960
"A man might have many encounters
throughout his life,

50
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,560
but there's only one person

51
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:28,720
who truly belongs to him and fits him.

52
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,920
If he can't find one,

53
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,200
he would just muddle along with his life.

54
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:34,720
It doesn't matter who he stays with.

55
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,200
He would be happy too.

56
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:41,880
But if you really find that one person…

57
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,200
It's like a sword

58
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,800
and its original scabbard.

59
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:49,240
Once they are on intimate terms…

60
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,920
If it loses its scabbard,

61
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,480
it will never find another one."

62
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:58,720
Isn't it just a scabbard?
It's not expensive.

63
