87
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,920
But…

88
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,960
But I hope…

89
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,800
to show you to many of my relatives.

90
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,880
I hope to let them know

91
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:39,960
that I have finally

92
