an idiot!

102
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:28,080
A right man?

103
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:31,280
I'm only here to take care of Chengling,

104
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,160
join in the fun,

105
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,680
and learn how to be a better human.

106
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:37,360
Sword and scabbard?

107
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,680
Idiot.

108
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:52,520
HANBI PAVILION

109
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,240
Long and long the white hair is,

110
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:59,320
everlasting my sorrow could be.

111
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:07,320
Master, we have sorted the medicine out.

112
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:09,480
