123
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,640
I'll leave now.

124
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:48,880
Qianqiao.

125
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:53,440
Master, do you have any commands?

126
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,720
Remember to bring your rain gear.

127
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,120
There will be heavy rain tomorrow.

128
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,680
