129
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:12,640
GREAT WISDOM

130
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,160
Elder Huang.

131
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,520
I'm sorry for coming this early

132
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,680
without prior notice.

133
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:23,480
Chief Yu, a nobleman should never come
to such an inferior place.

134
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:26,040
You're the chief of the Mount Hua Sect.

135
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,840
Why are you here

136
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:30,920
at the beggars' territory
so early in the morning?

137
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,680
I'm here today

138
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:35,000
to bring some gifts to the Beggar Gangs.

139
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,840
Really?

140
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:43,280
Your Mount Hua Sect and my Beggar Gangs

141
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,960
are not that close.

142
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,360
Chief Yu.

143
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:51,040
Do you know
that Gao Chong has turned against me?

144
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,920
Aren't you afraid that your master

145
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:57,080
will be mad at you
because of our interaction?

146
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:02,400
