and treated my enemy as a friend.

147
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,800
I'll take the blame

148
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:07,160
if you look down on me.

149
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:10,040
But nothing can beat
the grief of losing my son.

150
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:12,800
Even if I'm good-for-nothing,

151
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:15,040
I will never let them get away from it.

152
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:20,840
Who had the guts to kill the son
of Mount Hua Sect's chief?

153
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,280
Is it Ghost Valley?

154
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:25,560
It's the Five Lakes Alliance!

155
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:41,360
This Soul Winding Spell is indeed useful.

156
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,640
Long-Tongued Ghost didn't lie to me.

157
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:46,240
How could you, the lowly Mount Hua Sect,

158
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,960
dare to touch the Glazed Armor?

159
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,680
You have no proof.

160
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,040
The witness had died.

161
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:57,120
And you lost your evidence.

162
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,840
Just by your words

163
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:02,040
and its connection
with the Soul Winding Spell…

164
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:05,280
Even if the Mount Tai Sect
makes an accusation,

165
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:08,240
it's still hard to overthrow

166
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,960
the chief of the Five Lakes Alliance.

167
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:15,520
Elder Huang, I know another big secret.

168
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:19,640
It's enough to ruin the reputation
of Gao Chong and the Five Lakes Alliance.

169
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:21,800
