170
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:22,960
Twenty years ago,

171
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:25,240
the Five Lakes Alliance
with heroes around the world

172
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,880
punished Rong Xuan,
who had become a demon.

173
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:29,800
After Rong Xuan died,
the alliance secretly split

174
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,600
the five pieces of the Armor
among themselves.

175
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,640
Each of them hid a piece.

176
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,400
Those heroes

177
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,800
didn't even know that their sacrifices

178
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:39,480
were a waste of effort
to fulfill the greed

179
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:40,520
of those people!

180
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,040
Elder Huang,

181
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,440
many died in the Beggar Gangs,

182
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:47,640
not because of us,
the Five Mount and Sword Sects.

183
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,120
Once this is exposed,

184
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:55,800
the Five Lakes Alliance
might not collapse right away,

185
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,880
but they will lose the right to rule

186
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,640
the rest of the Glazed Armor pieces.

187
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,560
In terms of morality and ability,

188
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:04,120
the Beggar Gangs are most suitable

189
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,640
to lead the martial arts world.

190
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:09,360
By then, we shall force the alliance
to hand over their Glazed Armor

191
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:13,240
and let the Beggar Gangs lead the heroes
to fight against the Ghost Valley.

192
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:17,040
Even a coward

193
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:20,040
is turning his back
on the Five Lakes Alliance now.

194
00:12:20,680 --> 00:12:23,040
The trend has changed.

195
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:25,680
Gao Chong is coming to his end.

196
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:33,320
GOOD LUCK INN

